        "step-03",
        "step-04",
        "step-05",
        "step-07"
      ],
      "step_type": "velocity_calculation",
      "summary": "Combine spectrophotometric distances, radial velocities, and Gaia EDR3 proper motions to compute Cartesian galactocentric positions (x, y, z) and velocities (v_x, v_y, v_z) in a right-handed frame with the Sun on the negative x-axis, using solar position and motion from step-07.",
