          "start_line": 157,
          "end_line": 159,
          "context": "The spectrophotometric distances and radial velocities were combined with proper motions from Gaia EDR3 to trace back the trajectories ..."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "step-08",
      "depends_on": [],
      "step_type": "galactic_potential_model",
      "summary": "Milky Way mass model I of Irrgang et al. (2013): analytical three-component potential (central spherical bulge, axisymmetric disk, spherical dark matter halo). Model reproduces Galactic rotation curve and other constraints. Local escape velocity v_esc computed from the potential.",
